chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec6d354ac86a549d87de6b21334dc49393a6dc2f","tid":385732,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T04:04:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓豬有冇米7🤔</blockquote><br />\n收皮啦你</blockquote><br />\n咁有冇米6 有喇掛🤔</blockquote><br />\n米9男人都唔會carry到女人衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}